        'Life-threatening combinations: Sildenafil + nitrates, MAOIs + SSRIs, warfarin + multiple drugs',
        'St. John\'s Wort: Potent CYP3A4 inducer, decreases levels of immunosuppressants, contraceptives',
        'High-risk populations: Elderly (polypharmacy), renal impairment, multiple medications'
